## Common Patterns

<CardGrid>
<Card title="I2C Sensors">
Use `Wire.begin(sda, scl)` to set custom I2C pins before `sensor.begin()`. ESP32 defaults are GPIO 21 (SDA) and GPIO 22 (SCL).
